trans-unit.source: Defines a metadata attribute that is used to specify the number of allowed instances of a template.
trans-unit.target: 定義中繼資料屬性，用來指定允許的樣板執行個體化數目。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class allows you to mark a template property as one that allows single or multiple instantiations.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別可讓您將標示為允許單一或多個具現化樣板屬性。

trans-unit.source: A template that only allows a single instantiation can have the controls that are contained inside of it referenced.
trans-unit.target: 只允許單一具現化的範本可以包含在參考其內部的控制項。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property is an example of a property that can be instantiated only one time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>屬性是屬性，可以是具現化一次的範例。

trans-unit.source: This <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class is optional.
trans-unit.target: 這<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>是選擇性的類別。

trans-unit.source: If a template property is not extended with a <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class, the default value, the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Multiple> field, is used.
trans-unit.target: 如果樣板屬性不會延長<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別，預設值，<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Multiple>欄位，則會使用。

trans-unit.source: For more information about using attributes, see [Attributes](~/docs/standard/attributes/index.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需屬性用法的詳細資訊，請參閱[屬性](~/docs/standard/attributes/index.md)。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance> enumeration and the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance>列舉型別和<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別。

trans-unit.source: A custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control named `MyLoginViewA` overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.AnonymousTemplate%2A> property and uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class to specify that only one instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.AnonymousTemplate%2A> property is created.
trans-unit.target: 自訂<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>控制項，名為`MyLoginViewA`會覆寫<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.AnonymousTemplate%2A>屬性，並使用<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別，以指定只有一個執行個體<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.AnonymousTemplate%2A>會建立屬性。

trans-unit.source: The following code example is an ASPX file that uses the `MyLoginViewA` control and demonstrates how to access properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例會使用 ASPX 檔`MyLoginViewA`控制，並示範如何存取屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> 列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> class with the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 列舉值，初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Defines the default value for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 定義 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 類別的預設值。

trans-unit.source: This field is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 此欄位為唯讀。

trans-unit.source: The default behavior is to create multiple instances of the template using the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance.Multiple> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: 若要建立的範本使用多個執行個體的預設行為是<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance.Multiple>列舉值。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Object" /> to test.
trans-unit.target: 要測試的 <see cref="T:System.Object" />。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the specified object is a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object and is identical to the this <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 指出指定的物件是否為 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件，並且和這個 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件相同。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if value is both a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object and is identical to the this <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果值是 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件並且與這個 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 相同，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a hash code for this <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得這個 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件的雜湊程式碼。

trans-unit.source: The hash code for this <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 這個 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件的雜湊程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> enumeration value that the current template instance represents.
trans-unit.target: 取得目前樣板執行個體表示的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> 列舉值。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> enumeration value that the current template instance represents.
trans-unit.target: 目前範本執行個體所表示的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance" /> 列舉值。

trans-unit.source: The possible values are either the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Single> field or the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance.Multiple> field.
trans-unit.target: 可能的值都是<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Single>欄位或<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstance.Multiple>欄位。

trans-unit.source: In the `Page_Load` event of an ASPX page, the `MyLoginViewA` custom control's <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class for the `AnonymousTemplate` property is queried.
trans-unit.target: 在`Page_Load`ASPX 網頁，事件`MyLoginViewA`自訂控制項<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別`AnonymousTemplate`屬性進行查詢。

trans-unit.target: 定義的`MyLoginViewA`控制，請參閱<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>。

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating if the current <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object is the same as the default <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 傳回一個值，以指示目前的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件是否和預設的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 物件相同。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of the current instance of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> is the default; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" />目前的執行個體值為預設值，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default value for the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class is the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Multiple> field.
trans-unit.target: 預設值為<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別是<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Multiple>欄位。

trans-unit.source: In the `Page_Load` event of an ASPX page, the `MyLoginViewA` custom control's <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute> class for the `AnonymousTemplate` property is queried.
trans-unit.target: 在`Page_Load`ASPX 網頁，事件`MyLoginViewA`自訂控制項<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>類別`AnonymousTemplate`屬性進行查詢。

trans-unit.source: For the definition of the `MyLoginViewA` control, see <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: 定義的`MyLoginViewA`控制，請參閱<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute>。

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> class as one representing a template that will be instantiated multiple times.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 類別的執行個體，表示將多次執行個體化的樣板。

trans-unit.source: This field is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 此欄位為唯讀。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Multiple> field is accessed, a new template instance is instantiated multiple times.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Multiple>存取欄位，新的範本執行個體具現化多次。

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> class as one representing a template that will be instantiated a single time.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute" /> 類別的執行個體，表示將單次執行個體化的樣板。

trans-unit.source: This field is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 此欄位為唯讀。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Single> field is accessed, a new template instance is instantiated a single time.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateInstanceAttribute.Single>存取欄位，新的範本執行個體具現化一次。
